N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 79-7.3 - [Effective 12/22/2025] Experience requirements

State Regulations

An applicant shall meet the experience requirement for
licensure by completing the practicum, or clinical or work experience which the
applicant must complete as part of the professional education requirements for
licensure, as prescribed in section
79-7.2
of this

Subpart. Notes
